  <name>DLT Viewer</name>
  <summary>Diagnostic Log and Trace viewing program</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Read, inspect and analyze logs of Embedded Control Units (ECU) tipically found in the automotive field. DLT Viewer is based on the AUTOSAR 4.0 standard DLT.</p>
    <p>You can:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Fetch logs via TCP, UDP, and serial ports</li>
      <li>Filter logs depending on ECU, application, context, payload and more</li>
      <li>Search for keywords on filtered messages</li>
      <li>Mark log messages with colours</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
